#!patch

Consider any mail addres local, so clients can assign any name in their
nameserver toa the box's IP, only allow local users with a .forward file
(so only the mail user, e.g.  not archivista, or root) and no system aliases.

  - Rene Rebe <rene@exactcode.de>

